{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7986bdc690","title":"在陕甘宁边区工业展览会开幕式上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c406771698","index":0,"year":1939,"month":4,"day":29,"articleId":"7986bdc690"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ccd9085a78","type":"paragraph","text":"在陕甘宁边区工业展览会","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"7986bdc690"},{"id":"2b437eab9c","type":"paragraph","text":"开幕式上的讲话","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"7986bdc690"},{"id":"06967cde37","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年4月29日）现在全国的工作是什么？是打日本，建设新中国，所以叫“抗战建国”。要打倒日本帝国主义，必须有政治、军事、经济、文化各方面的新的建设。陕甘宁边区的政治建设、军事建设、经济建设、文化建设都搞得很好。这次工业展宽中，有重工业、轻工业，有大工业、小工业，在边区这样困难的条件下做出这些成绩来，是非常有意义的。H这是毛泽东在院甘宁边区工业展览会开幕式上讲话的一部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"7986bdc690"}],"page":{"id":"1eff2183b9","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"7986bdc690","start":289,"end":289}}}},"__N_SSG":true}